  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "As outline in a fork choice spec, an incoming attestation that is asserted as invalid may be valid at a later time. A node should keep it around and consider scheduling it for later processing. In our implementation, the node simply discards the invalid attestation and loses it for later processing. This could contribute to the unresolvable fork issue",
